---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Domain Echo | 100% Anonymous Chat"
  description="Domain Echo Privacy Policy: We don't track, store, or collect personal data. Learn how we protect your privacy with anonymous chat and zero data collection."
  keywords="privacy policy, anonymous chat privacy, no tracking, data protection, privacy-first extension"
  canonicalUrl="/privacy"
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950 to-slate-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">Last updated: February 9, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            At Domain Echo, we take your privacy seriously. This policy explains what information we collect (spoiler: very little), how we use it, and your rights regarding your data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">What We DO Collect:</h3>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Random Username</strong> - A randomly generated username (e.g., "CosmicPikachu777") stored locally in your browser</li>
            <li><strong>Messages</strong> - Chat messages you send, associated with your random username</li>
            <li><strong>Domain Information</strong> - The domain of the website you're chatting on (e.g., "example.com")</li>
            <li><strong>Presence Data</strong> - Temporary data showing you're active on a domain (automatically deleted after inactivity)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">What We DON'T Collect:</h3>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-2">
            <li>❌ Your real name or email address</li>
            <li>❌ Your IP address</li>
            <li>❌ Your browsing history</li>
            <li>❌ Cookies or tracking pixels</li>
            <li>❌ Any personally identifiable information (PII)</li>
            <li>❌ Analytics or usage data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The minimal data we collect is used solely to provide the Domain Echo service:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-2">
            <li>✅ Display your messages in chat rooms</li>
            <li>✅ Show who's currently active on a domain</li>
            <li>✅ Enable real-time communication</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            We do NOT use your data for advertising, marketing, or any other purpose.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Data Storage and Retention</h2>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-3">
            <li><strong>Messages:</strong> Stored temporarily in our database. We may implement automatic deletion of old messages.</li>
            <li><strong>Presence Data:</strong> Automatically deleted after 5 minutes of inactivity.</li>
            <li><strong>Username:</strong> Stored locally in your browser only. We don't store it on our servers.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            We do NOT sell, rent, or share your data with third parties. Period.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            The only "sharing" that occurs is when your messages are displayed to other users in the same chat room - which is the entire point of the service!
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Domain Echo uses Convex as our backend infrastructure provider. Convex may collect minimal technical data necessary to provide their service. Please review <a href="https://www.convex.dev/privacy" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">Convex's Privacy Policy</a> for more information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Since we don't collect personal information, there's not much to manage! However, you can:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-2">
            <li>✅ Reset your random username at any time in the extension settings</li>
            <li>✅ Clear your local data by clearing your browser's extension storage</li>
            <li>✅ Uninstall the extension to stop using the service</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Domain Echo is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children. If you believe a child has used Domain Echo, please contact us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-indigo-400 mt-2">
            <a href="mailto:kentaylorappdev@gmail.com" class="hover:text-indigo-300 transition">kentaylorappdev@gmail.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

